    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Insidious indeed. Thanks for explaining it. The trick mentioned is good work around.\n\nOne other tip: to display options in a particular order in the updated view (in my case alphanumerically) set `w.options = []` and then set `w.options` as desired. Otherwise the new options are just appended to the current ones in the view.\n"
